          p(strong("Prof. Stapel's note:"), " \"Last challenge! This tests whether you understand your responsibilities as a researcher. You've learned about preventing problems through preregistration, power analysis, and open data. But what if you discover problems in published work during your literature review? This is about scientific integrity and your duty to the field...\"")
